，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"0ed347552c3178d1ae378bc9c1a299af235a844e","tid":1775832,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"sweden比較貴 應該多嘢玩過finland 但我鍾意finland多啲 不過真係旅行嘅話應該會悶啲"},{"pid":"7a788e78354da9c68fb1b399da1d7f0c6ffb6693","tid":1775832,"uid":218289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"請教下各位<br />\nRovaniemi / Trosmo / Abisko<br />\n北極圈城市去邊個好？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbbfe8440dea6e40f1fc1bd0903798b1aa523ba","tid":1775832,"uid":68231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65652ec9038c684e911d604b3a25740034c61dec","tid":1775832,"uid":158328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ba0ae558c5e9c1c393b4f3de74cbf066c9c794e","tid":1775832,"uid":54568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:02:57.000Z","msg":"可以去行下山Stavanger ,Bergen 附近有挪威三大奇石，之後Bergen可以坐Nutshell 去Oslo<br />\n<br />\nOslo唔好留太多日！<br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得北歐最正都係Iceland <br />\n<br />\n利申挪威exchange"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:15:16.000Z","msg":"挪威既話樓主仲可以揀去Lofoten, Troms&oslash;同附近既Abisko<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n非常agger層主話Oslo唔好留咁多日 個人覺得1日起兩日止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n丹麥既話其實除咗Copenhagen之外都有乜特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n瑞典既話個人覺得Stockholm比同Oslo一樣咁悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要去到北面Abisko先會話有啲特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申Stockholm exchange緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"Lofoten 好遠<br />\n要